basics.summary: Hey, I'm a construction engineer turned software engineer and blockchain technology enthusiast, I like to build things that have strong impact. My latest web app was about building a dashboard for Parking company that helped sales to handle the subscriptions and retrieve data for future marketing purposes. Currently, I am volunteering working on application to handle bookings for a small hotel business with a challenge to do in React and MongoDB. I am opened to new propositions around back end/front end technologies.
